xis added a unique touch. I explored various versions of Cupcake in three backgrounds using Twinmotion’s [Path Tracer](https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/twinmotion/path-tracer-requirements-for-twinmotion). With computer design, Cupcake features palm trees for illustration on top and comprises four bowl-shaped sides.\n\nYou can also check the design on my [TikTok](https://www.tiktok.com/@arnottferels/photo/7332762183811484933).\n\n<div className=\"mdx-col-max-3\">\n  <ImgDefa>\n    ![Cupcake](./figures/cupcake-01.png \"Cupcake\")\n    </ImgDefa>\n  <ImgDefa>\n    ![Cupcake](./figures/cupcake-02.png \"Cupcake\")\n    </ImgDefa>\n  <ImgDefa>\n    ![Cupcake](./figures/cupcake-03.png \"Cupcake\")\n  </ImgDefa>\n  <ImgDefa>\n    ![Cupcake](./figures/cupcake-04.png \"Cupcake\")\n    </ImgDefa>\n  <ImgDefa>\n    ![Cupcake](./figures/cupcake-05.png \"Cupcake\")\n    </ImgDefa>\n  <ImgDefa>\n    ![Cupcake](./figures/cupcake-06.png \"Cupcake\")\n  </ImgDefa>\n  <ImgDefa>\n    ![Cupcake](./figures/cupcake-07.png \"Cupcake\")\n    </ImgDefa>\n  <ImgDefa>\n    ![Cupcake](./figures/cupcake-08.png \"Cupcake\")\n    </ImgDefa>\n  <ImgDefa>\n    ![Cupcake](./figures/cupcake-09.png \"Cupcake\")\n  </ImgDefa>\n</div>\n","tableOfContents":{}}},"pageContext":{"id":"52ba7e8c-5dc8-5bb9-ae88-f83a51b0bf2e","frontmatter__p_type":"models","frontmatter__slug":"cupcake","__params":{"frontmatter__p_type":"models","frontmatter__slug":"cupcake"},"frontmatter":{"p_type":"models","title":"Cupcake","slug":"cupcake","date":"2023-11","hero_img_src":"./figures/cupcake-01.png","hero_img_alt":"Cupcake","hero_img_crd_txt":"Arnott Ferels","hero_img_crd_link":"/","keywords":[{"id":1,"name":"Design Exploration"},{"id":2,"name":"Algoritmic Design"},{"id":3,"name":"Cupcake"}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["116989619","2484020538","3159585216","460926906"],"slicesMap":{}}